                <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 font-medium">Our Basic Secretarial package includes automatic Confirmation Statement filing and deadline reminders every year.</p>
                <a href="/pricing" class="btn-primary inline-block">View Secretarial Plans</a>
            </div>
